# Edit Page Component Style

Use this structure and styling for edit/form pages (e.g. pricelist-edit, sp-provider). Keeps consistent look and feel.

## Page Header

- Title on left, 2 buttons on right: **Назад** (goBack), **Сохранить** (save)
- Buttons: `header-btn` class, `save-btn` for primary save button
- Назад: secondary style (gray)
- Сохранить: primary (blue), with mat-icon save

```html
<div class="page-header">
  <h1 class="page-title">{{ headerTitle }}</h1>
  <div class="header-actions">
    <button mat-raised-button class="header-btn" (click)="goBack()">Назад</button>
    <button mat-raised-button color="primary" class="header-btn save-btn" (click)="save()" [disabled]="loading">
      <mat-icon>save</mat-icon>
      Сохранить
    </button>
  </div>
</div>
```

## Data Card (2 columns per row)

- `mat-card` with `data-card` class
- `mat-card-header` with `mat-card-title` and optional `mat-card-subtitle`
- `mat-card-content` with `form-row` divs
- **Each form-row**: 2 items (grid 1fr 1fr)
- `mat-form-field` with `form-field` class, `appearance="outline"`

```html
<mat-card class="data-card">
  <mat-card-header>
    <mat-card-title>Заголовок секции</mat-card-title>
    <mat-card-subtitle>Описание секции (опционально).</mat-card-subtitle>
  </mat-card-header>
  <mat-card-content>
    <div class="form-row">
      <mat-form-field class="form-field" appearance="outline">
        <mat-label>Название</mat-label>
        <input matInput [(ngModel)]="item.name" required>
      </mat-form-field>
      <mat-form-field class="form-field" appearance="outline">
        <mat-label>Код</mat-label>
        <input matInput [(ngModel)]="item.code">
      </mat-form-field>
    </div>
  </mat-card-content>
</mat-card>
```

## Layout Rules

| Element | Style |
|---------|-------|
| **Container** | `padding: 20px`, `max-width: 1200px`, `margin: 0 auto` |
| **Page header** | `border-bottom: 2px solid #e0e0e0`, `padding-bottom: 16px` |
| **Page title** | `font-size: 28px`, `color: #333` |
| **Header buttons** | `min-width: 150px`, `height: 40px`, `@include button-primary` / `button-secondary` |
| **Data card** | `border-radius: 8px`, `box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)` |
| **Card header** | `background: #f8f9fa`, `padding: 16px 20px` |
| **Card subtitle** | `mat-card-subtitle` — описание под заголовком |
| **Form row** | `grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr`, `gap: 20px` |
| **Form field** | `width: 100%` |

